query:
SELECT c.id, c.tentId, t.name as tentName, c.cloningStartDate, c.floraStartDate, c.status
FROM cycles c
JOIN tents t ON c.tentId = t.id
WHERE c.status = 'ACTIVE'
ORDER BY c.id;
